# Code owners for fish-ai-git.
#
# These paths cover the code that actually ships to users' machines and the
# CI/release machinery that guards it. Requiring owner review on changes here
# makes an unreviewed change to shipped code stand out. Combined with branch
# protection (see SECURITY.md), it forces every such change through a public,
# reviewed PR.

# Shipped functions and event handlers (run on user machines).
/functions/       @Guernik
/conf.d/          @Guernik

# The audit scanner and its runner.
/scripts/         @Guernik
/justfile         @Guernik

# CI and release workflows, and this ownership file itself.
/.github/         @Guernik

# Security policy and verification instructions.
/SECURITY.md      @Guernik
